<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>User Reviews</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 20px;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        h1, p {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding-left: 0;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        input[type="button"] {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin-right: 10px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            background-color: #7D1CAD;
            color: white;
        }

        input[type="button"]:hover {
            background-color: #4d1a9c;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>선택한<%= userName %>님의 평점은 <%= userRating %>이며</h1>
    <p>리뷰는 다음과 같습니다:</p>
    <ul>
        <% for (let i = 0; i < userReviews.length; i++) { %>
            <li><%= userReviews[i] %></li>
        <% } %>
    </ul>

    <p>예약을 진행하시겠습니까?</p>
    <input type="button" value="예약하기" onclick="location.href='/reservation'">
    <input type="button" value="다시 선택하기" onclick="location.href='/ExpertFilter'">
</body>
</html>
